            <h3 class="step-heading bg-dk-blue">Step 2: Resale</h3>
            <div class="step-body">
                <p>Combine your existing portfolio with our suite of mobility services to create an integrated solution for your customers. An enhanced product offering can help you:</p>
                <ul class="has_bullets">
                    <li>Provide one-stop shopping for your customers</li>
                    <li>Increase revenue streams</li>
                    <li>Reduce churn and deactivations</li>
                    <li>Enhance your customer base</li>
                </ul>

                <hr class="blue_hr" />
            
                <!-- Document List: Use Cases -->
                <h3 class="bg-heading"><apex:image value="{!URLFOR($Resource.ImgStatic,'/ico-head-clipboard.svg')}" />Use Cases</h3>
                <apex:outputPanel >   
                    <apex:repeat value="{!DocMapUseCases}" var="docMap"> 
                        <apex:outputLink value="{!fileURL}+{!docMap.id}" target="_blank" styleClass="document-file">
