        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="row stepCont step4-cont">
            <h3 class="step-heading bg-dk-gray">Step 4: Applications</h3>
            <div class="step-body">
                <p>Applications are a perfect complement to {!$Label.Mobile_Services}. They can help speed up communications and increase productivity for mobile workers in any industry.</p>
                <!-- FIXME: need to show correct active tab for Mobile > Learn More > Applications link -->
                <p>Learn more about <a data-page="PortalDesign_Mobile_Learn_Applications" href="#PortalDesign_Mobile_Learn_Applications">Applications</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="row stepCont step5-cont">
            <h3 class="step-heading bg-blue">Step 5: Internet of Things&nbsp;(IoT)</h3>
            <div class="step-body">
                <p>The Internet of Things (IoT) is transforming the way we live and work.</p>
                <p>IoT solutions from AT&amp;T can help you accelerate your time to market, run your operations more efficiently, and optimize the profitability of your connected device initiatives.</p>
                <p>Learn more about the <a href="{!$Page.PortalDesign_IOT}">{!$Label.IOT}</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
